originalText.text: I was looking for a daycare where I can feel secure when leaving my daughter. But most importantly a place that my daughter feels at home because she was recently diagnosed with Autism and she does not tolerate changes very well. The first time we went to check Zulai Daycare, my daughter start playing with all the toys Zulai’s has, explored the whole room and did not want to leave. I knew at that moment that I entered the right daycare for my daughter. It took less time than I expected for my daughter to get use to the new daycare. Zulai is very caring, and have a lot of patience. I like that she offers a variety of healthy food, which help my daughter know different food. My daughter is always happy to go to Zulai and when I pick her up she is happy too. I like the communication with Zulai, she always keep me inform of everything and is always there to answer any questions. I love that she sends me picture of my daughter when I’m at work, it feels good knowing she is being well take care of. I would totally recommend Zulai Daycare to other parents.
